column16: Alcides Escobar doubles (2) on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Ryan Raburn.    Matt Treanor to 3rd.
Matt Treanor reaches on a fielder's choice out, first baseman Miguel Cabrera to third baseman Brandon Inge.    Wilson Betemit out at 3rd.
Wilson Betemit doubles (4) on a line drive to right fielder Brennan Boesch.
Billy Butler doubles (2) on a line drive to left fielder Ryan Raburn.    Alex Gordon to 3rd.
Alex Gordon singles on a line drive to right fielder Brennan Boesch.
Chris Getz grounds out, shortstop Jhonny Peralta to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
Alcides Escobar lines out to second baseman Will Rhymes.
Brayan Pena grounds out, second baseman Will Rhymes to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
